Downer - Entity NÂ° 0001
Mitch Myers b.1989

Tether resides in the phase of:  Exile 

A space of absolute isolation and abandonment. This tether holds the pain of loneliness and the fear of being forgotten; it can be both a source of suffering and a place of introspection. Those who are bound to this tether may feel alone and forgotten, but they may also use their isolation to explore their own inner world and find a sense of purpose and meaning.
